summary: I know Big Potato was pretty big before Dan and Phil but I’m really happy what Truth Bombs and Dan and Phil have done to help...
body:
I know Big Potato was pretty big before Dan and Phil but I’m really happy what Truth Bombs and Dan and Phil have done to help the company. It’s obvious they do it just for fun and it’s honestly wonderful and so genuine. That company has gotten table top games on the gaming channel and I love it.

And I love seeing the companies interactions with my friends online and how they get their little games and potatoes in the mail. Like yes be happy with your potatoe that’s so cute.

And the company just seems really cool and down to earth I can get behind a company like that. They interact enough with the fandom but they don’t push it.
